items.name: 胭脂梦_PinkDream【CCD系列】
items.description:
Rouge Dream_ PinkDream

-This is a "Light and Shadow Lora" that can give your images a romantic and gentle pink purple like sunset glow and a delicate and hazy soft light effect. The bright parts are slightly magenta, while the dark parts are cold purple, bringing a unique dreamy beauty to the screen;

-The overall saturation is low and comes with a depth of field effect. It handles the blurriness and deformation of the foreground, mid range, and vision very naturally. The edges of the objects in the picture are not very sharp, so they are closer to the real image;

-For the skin color of real people, exposure processing will be carried out, combined with a pink tone, so the skin of the person will appear particularly fair and translucent, making it very suitable for portrait photography. For scenes and still life, such as food or flowers, they are also very effective;

-The model has excellent generalization and can be used in combination with most large models or lora, regardless of realism, anime or 3D style. Weights between 0.6 and 1 are acceptable;

——————————-

-Which one can better express real life, clear and gorgeous or low-quality and rough? I'm afraid different scenarios have different answers. When we are proud, we wish that everyone and everything could be clearly controlled by ourselves. When we are struggling, we like to put ourselves in a shell and squint at the world. And this "Rouge Dream" Lora is looking for the feeling of real life under the roughness and haziness. The inspiration for its tone comes from the unique visual effects of CCD cameras, which express real life with roughness, particles, and haziness. Therefore, the author plans to launch a series of "light and shadow" models, including Lora, Big Model, or Lycoris, striving to achieve a balance between generalization, aesthetics, and reality for each model.

——————————-

Beautiful jade in a rough cask, half a life's dream of confused.

胭脂梦_PinkDream

- 这是一款【光影类lora】，可以让你的画面有着晚霞般浪漫温柔的粉紫色和细腻朦胧的柔光效果，亮部偏洋红色，暗部偏冷紫色，为画面中带来独特的梦幻美感；

- 整体饱和度偏低，自带景深效果，对于前景、中景和愿景的模糊度和变形度，处理的也非常自然，画面中的物体的边缘地方不会处理的很锐利，因此也更接近真实图片；

- 对于真实人物的肤色，会进行曝光处理，同时结合粉色调，所以会显得人物的皮肤特别白皙透亮，非常适合人像摄影。对于场景和静物，例如美食或者花卉，同样也非常出效果；

- 模型的泛化性非常出色，可以和绝大多数大模型或者lora结合使用，不限写实、二次元或3D风格。权重在0.6-1之间均可；

———————————

- 清晰艳丽和低品质粗糙，哪一个能更好的表达真实生活？恐怕不同的场景都有不同的答案。志得意满的时候，我们恨不得所有人和事都能被自己清晰的掌握，困苦潦倒的时候，喜欢把自己装在壳子里，眯着眼看世界。而这款“胭脂梦”lora就是在寻找粗糙与朦胧之下的真实生活的感受。其色调的灵感则来源于CCD相机的独特画面效果，用粗糙、颗粒和朦胧来表达真实生活。因此作者计划推出一系列的【光影】模型，包括Lora、大模型或者lycoris，力求每个模型都能达到泛化性、美感与真实的平衡。

———————————

美玉于陋椟，半生胭脂梦。

items.name: Comic expression : white eyes set A / 白目セットA
items.description:
(日本語説明は後半にあります)

Reproduces white eyes, a familiar cartoon/anime deformation expression.

4 types (Type 1 to Type 4) are available in this "Set A".

  • Type 1 : Larger regular circle shaped

  • Type 2 : Smaller regular circle shaped, with convex border

  • Type 3 : Vertical oval shaped

  • Type 4 : Cartoon styled eyes expressing anger

  • To download all types, switch version tabs ↑ above.

Set B (Type 5 to 8) is also available.

Easy to use. No trigger prompts are necessary.

Use with "IrisMix" checkpoint and use for "chibi" style characters is recommended. Not so suitable for realistic-style(2.5D/3D) models.

If it doesn't work well, try increasing LoRA weight.

Other shaped eyes LoRA series will be available soon (all types are already available on HuggingFace).

On my HuggingFace repo, you can download more various other LoRAs. please check it out.

https://huggingface.co/JujoHotaru/lora

漫画・アニメ的なデフォルメ表現でおなじみ、白目を再現できます。

セットAには4種類（タイプ1～4）が含まれます。各タイプをダウンロードするには、ページ上部のバージョンタブを切り替えてください。

  • Type 1 : 大きな正円形です。

  • Type 2 : Type 1より小さな正円形で、若干凹凸表現が入った雰囲気です。

  • Type 3 : 縦長楕円形です。

  • Type 4 : 怒り目を表現する吊り上がり形です。

セットB (Type 6～8) も公開しています。

アニメ(2D)系のデータモデル用です。リアル(2.5D/3D)系のデータモデルではほとんどの場合うまく動作しません。

検証において成功率が高かった"IrisMix"での使用を推奨します。

LoRAを有効にするだけで発動します。階層調整済みですので、基本的には階層指定せず強度指定のみで大丈夫です。うまく出ない場合は適用強度を上げてみてください。

ちびキャラを出すときは標準強度で充分効果がありますが、リアル頭身の場合は強度を1.1～1.5くらいまで強くしてみたほうが効果が出やすくなるようです。

他形状の眼シリーズも順序公開していきます（HuggingFaceではすでに全種類公開中です）。

HuggingFaceリポジトリでは、他にもさまざまなLoRAを公開しています。

items.name: Simple_XL
items.description:
This model appears to be capable of just about anything you ask of it. SFW, NSFW etc. etc. - It also follows the prompt rather well compared to many models. It looks fairly realistic, perhaps not the most realistic, but it doesn't suffer from the close-up syndrome that seems to plague many other realism models.

At 1024x1024, and similar resolutions at different aspect ratios, it produces good results. However best results are seen by further using it to refine the upscaled image. Somewhat like the hi-res Fix feature of Automatic1111. Almost all defects that may occur in anatomy (eyes/fingers) are corrected simply through this additional step.

I've not really tested it outside of realism, but I assume it is more than capable of any other styles also, much like most SDXL models with the right prompting. Considering how well it follows the prompt anyway, I doubt it will be much of an issue for anyone.


Support me here!

https://www.buymeacoffee.com/tripleheadg


--

This is a custom merge, the details of which I cannot remember fully. However, what I do remember is that I started with XL13 Asmodeus from Afroman and merged it with dreamshaper using the "add difference" option alongside a 3rd model. I can't for the life of me remember which model specifically it was - either protovision or maybe it was SpectrumBlend.

Either way, afterwards I took that merge and then merged that with Randommax's dark offset lora.


My intentions with this are to use it as a base model to train on top of. But the results it produces are so decent that I thought it would be a waste not to provide the community with it.

items.name: Kristen Hager - Textual Inversion
items.description:
This ti was requested by @loyar

Kristen Hager is a Canadian actress. One of her notable roles was as Nora Sergeant in the TV series "Being Human," a supernatural drama that aired from 2011 to 2014. She also appeared in the science fiction series "The Expanse" as Ade Nygaard. From 2018 to 2020, Kristen Hager played the role of Mae Barbe in the TV series "Condor," where she had a main role. "Condor" is a television adaptation of the novel "Six Days of the Condor" by James Grady, and it follows the story of a young CIA analyst who becomes embroiled in a deadly conspiracy. From 2021 to 2022, Kristen Hager was a part of the main cast of the TV series "Chicago Med." In the show, she portrayed the character Stevie Hammer. "Chicago Med" is a medical drama that is part of the "Chicago" franchise created by Dick Wolf. It follows the lives of doctors, nurses, and staff working at the fictional Gaffney Chicago Medical Center.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :) (I also do commissions)

items.name: Neringa Kriziute
items.description:
Activation of LoRa - <lora:NeringaCrisiute:0.75> nerkriz

LoRa is managing well. It is quite easy to replace clothes, hairstyle, hair color and so on. I tried to make LoRa convey not only the face and hairstyle, but also the figure of a person. The best matches I had were : weight LoRa 0.7-0.75, CFG - 4, STEPS -22 .

If you see any bugs in LoRa, do not hesitate to write to me about it. This will give me the opportunity to improve the results in the future.

If you need LoRa for someone - write in the comments. If I can, I will.

Активация лоры - <лора:НерингаКризиуте:0.75> nerkriz

Лора неплохо управляется. Довольно легко заменить одежду, прическу, цвет волос и прочее. Постарался сделать так чтобы лора передавала не только лицо и прическу ,но и фигуру человека. Наилучшие результаты у меня были : вес лоры 0,7-0,75 , CFG - 4, STEPS-22 .

Если вы видите какие-то баги в лоре - не стесняйтесь написать мне об этом. Это даст мне возможность улучшить результаты в будущем.

Если вам нужна лора на кого-либо - пишите в комментариях. Если смогу - сделаю.

items.name: SteamPunk Armor
items.description:
Full steam ahead!

At this point it feel kinda redundant to make a Steampunk themed clothing model since most checkpoint models can probably generate them even without LORAs. But since I already made them anyway and I need more space on my computer, I'm uploading it here lol..

Weight: 0.65 - 0.85

Trigger: steam4rmor, steampunk

Additional tags:

Just specify what kind of armor it is, like for example:

  • steampunk warrior armor

  • steampunk rogue armor

  • steampunk barbarian

  • steampunk priest robe

  • steampunk exosuit

  • etc.

And then just add armor or clothing prompts that's specific to the armor set. For example: "steampunk rogue armor, cloak, hood, dagger"

Side effect: May also create steam and smoke around character and background, try adding 'steam' and 'smoke' in the negative prompt to reduce the effect.

p/s: If you're leaving a review, consider sharing your generated images too. I love looking at your creations..

Buy me a coffee.. ☕

items.description:
国画 | 水墨 | 山水画

智者乐山山如画，仁者乐水水无涯。自古以来，已经有无数的文人墨客寄情山水，抒怀表志。时至今日，从喧哗的钢筋水泥中逃离，回到山林，早已成为很多人的假日情结。当身心疲惫到无法忍受时，心中的那个情结就愈发强烈——奔向山水之所在。

学学文人的情怀，远离市区的喧嚣，只为早晨起床，推开窗，看着远山的一抹浓绿，听着溪流的清脆声音，嗅着沁人心脾的花草馨香。这种享受，是城市永远不能给予的。

更让人心仪的是，当夜幕垂降，月盈如镜，树影弄姿，当真可以像古人一般“举杯邀明月，对影成三人”了。最惬意的度假方式，莫过于彻底放松身心，在山水的灵气间遇见另一个自己。

汇集了近代多位作家的作品，内容足够丰富，多彩，道友们尽情享受自己的山水之间吧；

自己摸索炼丹，技能拙劣，还在探索中，希望道友们多多指点。

欢迎各位道友入座指正点评，学习交流。

此次更新，补充了自己精心挑选的素材，画风独特，唯美，让人沉溺于其中，流连忘返。

Traditional Chinese Painting | Ink Painting | Landscape Painting

The wise find joy in picturesque mountains, while the virtuous find delight in boundless waters. Since ancient times, countless literati and poets have expressed their emotions through landscape, expressing their thoughts and aspirations. Even today, escaping from the noise of steel and concrete to return to the mountains and forests has become a holiday yearning for many. When one is exhausted beyond endurance, that yearning in the heart becomes stronger - to seek solace in the embrace of nature.

Learning from the sentiment of literati, distancing oneself from the hustle of the city, just to wake up in the morning, open the window, gaze at the rich green of distant mountains, listen to the crisp sound of a stream, and inhale the refreshing fragrance of flowers and grass. This kind of enjoyment is something the city can never provide.

What's even more delightful is when night falls, the moon shines like a mirror, tree shadows sway gracefully, and one can truly "raise a cup to invite the bright moon, and share the shadows with the companions." The most enjoyable way to vacation is to completely relax body and mind, and meet another self within the spirit of the landscape.

items.name: [Anime-based LoRA] Chtholly Nota Seniorious/クトリセニオリス (Shuumatsu Nani Shitemasu ka? Isogashii desu ka?)
items.description:
This is our first fully-automatically-trained LoRA based on anime video, instead. More anime-baed LoRA is coming ...

  • THIS MODEL HAS TWO FILES. YOU NEED TO USE THEM TOGETHER!!!

  • The associated trigger words are only for reference, it may need to be adjusted at some times.

  • The recommended weight for the embedding model is 1, which provides higher fidelity; if greater generalization is required, it can be lowered to 0.5.

  • The recommended weight for the LoRA model is 0.85; if there's evidence of contamination, consider lowering it to 0.6.

How to Use This Model

THIS MODEL HAS TWO FILES. YOU NEED TO USE THEM TOGETHER!!!. In this case, you need to download both chtholly_sukasuka.pt and chtholly_sukasuka.safetensors, then use chtholly_sukasuka.pt as texture inversion embedding, and use chtholly_sukasuka.safetensors as LoRA at the same time.

このモデルには2つのファイルがあります。一緒に使う必要があります！！！。 この場合、chtholly_sukasuka.ptとchtholly_sukasuka.safetensorsの両方をダウンロード する必要があります。chtholly_sukasuka.ptをテクスチャ反転埋め込みとして使用し、同時にchtholly_sukasuka.safetensorsをLoRAとして使用してください。

这个模型有两个文件。你需要同时使用它们！！！。 在这种情况下，您需要下载chtholly_sukasuka.pt和chtholly_sukasuka.safetensors这两个文件，然后将chtholly_sukasuka.pt用作纹理反转嵌入， 同时使用chtholly_sukasuka.safetensors作为LoRA。

이 모델은 두 개의 파일이 있습니다. 두 파일을 함께 사용해야 합니다!!!. 이 경우에는 chtholly_sukasuka.pt와 chtholly_sukasuka.safetensors 두 파일을 모두 다운로드하신 다음에 chtholly_sukasuka.pt을 텍스처 반전 임베딩으로 사용하고, 동시에 chtholly_sukasuka.safetensors을 LoRA로 사용하셔야 합니다.

(Translated with ChatGPT)

The trigger word is chtholly_sukasuka, and the recommended tags are best quality, masterpiece, highres, solo, {chtholly_sukasuka:1.15}, blue_hair, long_hair, blue_eyes, two_side_up, multicolored_hair.

How This Model Is Trained

This model is trained with HCP-Diffusion. And the auto-training framework is maintained by DeepGHS Team.

Why Some Preview Images Not Look Like Chtholly Sukasuka

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is adjusting the tags you are using.

I Felt This Model May Be Overfitting or Underfitting, What Shall I Do

Our model has been published on huggingface repository - CyberHarem/chtholly_sukasuka, where models of all the steps are saved. Also, we published the training dataset on huggingface dataset - CyberHarem/chtholly_sukasuka, which may be helpful to you.

Why Not Just Using The Better-Selected Images

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention. It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

Why Can't the Desired Character Outfits Be Accurately Generated

Our current training data is sourced from various image websites, and for a fully automated pipeline, it's challenging to accurately predict which official images a character possesses. Consequently, outfit generation relies on clustering based on labels from the training dataset in an attempt to achieve the best possible recreation. We will continue to address this issue and attempt optimization, but it remains a challenge that cannot be completely resolved. The accuracy of outfit recreation is also unlikely to match the level achieved by manually trained models.

In fact, this model's greatest strengths lie in recreating the inherent characteristics of the characters themselves and its relatively strong generalization capabilities, owing to its larger dataset. As such, this model is well-suited for tasks such as changing outfits, posing characters, and, of course, generating NSFW images of characters!😉".

For the following groups, it is not recommended to use this model and we express regret:

  1. Individuals who cannot tolerate any deviations from the original character design, even in the slightest detail.

  2. Individuals who are facing the application scenarios with high demands for accuracy in recreating character outfits.

  3. Individuals who cannot accept the potential randomness in AI-generated images based on the Stable Diffusion algorithm.

  4. Individuals who are not comfortable with the fully automated process of training character models using LoRA, or those who believe that training character models must be done purely through manual operations to avoid disrespecting the characters.

  5. Individuals who finds the generated image content offensive to their values.

items.name: 涟漪荡漾 | 水神共工氏Gonggongshi
items.description:
Water God Gonggongshi_V1.0

Since learning AI, anyone who knows Gonggongshi must know its original author chocolae, and I have long admired his people, especially his Gonggongshi Lora.

Since I have seen its special effects, I thought that when I have the ability to make a cool Lora .......

So, I practiced day and night to make a raw image, studied and watched tutorials, and did my best to understand the underlying logic of this knowledge.

The initial intention of the creation originated from the imitation of the model, so I have been looking for information on this kind of magic, to understand how this kind of special effects are generated, and how to communicate with the figure, and so on almost understand the idea of it after ..........

So there will be "water god Gonggongshi Gonggongshi_V1.0".

Water God Gonggongshi Gonggongshi_V1.0, in fact, has been the equivalent of my current ability to release the finished product, the first draft is about 20 types of line drawings in the MJ refining, and then through the addition of magic and GLOW 2.5D model combined with the map, selected 70 of the pictures I feel more satisfied with the re-production. Considering that the previously released LORA "FireMan_V1.0" used a DIM value of 64, which is still lacking some details in the generation of special effects, so this time the DIM value used in the refining is 128, which is a bit more refined in the learning process.

This Lora is still the previous period of ancient mythological characters, in order to continue this style, the solid named "Water God Gonggongshi_V1.0", the ancient mythological character "Gonggong" as a concept of prosperity and become.

Gonggong, also known as Gonggong's, Kang Hui, Kong Ren, is the god of water in ancient Chinese mythology. He was a descendant of Emperor Yan Di and the son of Zhu Rong. In early literature, Gong Gong was a vassal of Yao, then evolved into an ancient emperor and tribal leader, and later transformed into the mythological god of the heavens who angrily crashed into the Buzhou Mountain, destroying the order of the heavenly bodies. Gong Gong's era can be traced back to the Gaoxin clan, Zhuanxu, the Yellow Emperor, and the Yan Emperor, and then to the Shun and Yu periods.

The base film used by Lora is GhostMax 2.0 combined with water and wave effects. Although it is a 2.5D base model, I have also tested other mainstream big models, and the result is quite good:

(masterpiece,topquality,best quality,official art,beautiful and aesthetic:1.2)

1girl or 1boy,upper body, blurry background, Blue theme.

<lora:Water God Gonggongshi:0.8>,shuishen,gonggongshi,water,waves, (masterpiece,topquality,official art,beautiful and aesthetic:1.2)

Today just out of Dan, out of the picture is limited, I hope you can give me back some pictures to show your personal creativity of the picture, thank you ......

水神共工氏Gonggongshi_V1.0

自学AI以来，凡知御水必定知道它的原作者chocolae，我对其人也是仰慕已久，特别是他的御水Lora。

自从看过它的特效后，当时就想等自己有能力了也一定要练制一个这样炫酷的Lora......

于是，没日没夜的练习生图，不段的学习看教程，尽能力去了解这些知识的底层逻辑，

创作的初衷源自于仿模，于是一直找这种魔法的资料，了解这种特效是如何生成，又是如何与图洽接，等差不多理解了它的思路后..........

于是便有了“水神共工氏Gonggongshi_V1.0”。

水神共工氏Gonggongshi_V1.0，其实已经是相当于我目前所能发布的成品了，初稿是用20张左右的类型于线稿的MJ图炼制，再通过加魔法与GLOW 2.5D大模型结合出图，选取了其中70张个人感觉比较满意的图片再制而成。考虑到之前发布的LORA“火神祝融氏FireMan_V1.0”使用的DIM值为64，在特效生成方面还是差一些细节，所以这次炼制使用的DIM值为128，感觉在学习上可能更精细一些。

这个Lora是依然是以往期上古神话人物为主，为延续这类风格，固取名“水神共工氏Gonggongshi_V1.0”，以上古神话人物“共工”做为一个概念繁生而成的。

共工，又名共工氏、康回、孔壬，中国古代神话中的水神。炎帝后裔，祝融之子。在早期的文献中，共工是尧的臣子，之后演变为古帝王、部落首领，后再转变为神话中怒撞不周山、破坏天体秩序的天神。共工所处的时代，往前可追溯至高辛氏、颛顼、黄帝、炎帝等时期，往后则流传至舜、禹时期。

Lora使用的底膜为GhostMax2.0版结合水及波浪效果练制。虽然是以2.5D的底模炼制，但我也测试过其它主流的大模型，出图效果尚佳以下为测试的TAGS：
